{"tid":2438352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當局收到45宗接種新冠疫苗後涉住院及嚴重等異常事件","createTime":"2021-03-08T12:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9da876a1269eb9d2ca3fba9ec64073f27bc5c0ab","tid":2438352,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579445-20210308.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579445-20210308.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=a22a3db3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579445-20210308.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4bd8b209\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579445-20210308.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會就3宗懷疑與接種疫苗後出現嚴重異常事件報告舉行會議。衞生防護中心總監林文健表示，截至昨日下午4時，共收到45宗涉及住院及嚴重等異常事件；另外收到16宗非嚴重異常事件，主要是頭痛、疲倦等。<br />\n<br />\n委員會共同召集人孔繁毅表示，根據2018年數據，本港平均每日有1.3人死於糖尿病或相關併發症，而死於冠心病及腦血管疾病，平均每日分別有10.3人及8.3人，70歲以上人士死亡率顯著增加；至於大動脈撕裂個案，全年有369宗、即平均每日一宗。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，去年錄得約7300宗因心肌梗塞入院個案；因急性中風入院個案約有10300宗。"},{"pid":"744db85da94cf20bf9d915927a9e77611344fbaf","tid":2438352,"uid":65297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:31:05.000Z","msg":"其他愛國者去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4317cd735b0f6dec0f6e261dd8d73773649aec","tid":2438352,"uid":6192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:34:57.000Z","msg":"講咁撚大篇野都係想講<br />\n日日都有人死架喇<br />\n關支疫苗撚事咩<br />\n有針你班廢老就死黎打喇"},{"pid":"c77e3471e8921a64ba4b678eb770550a9b7fab2d","tid":2438352,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5TTJntC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TTJntC.gif&h=14c301a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bsq36Vh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBsq36Vh.gif&h=f249878d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsXRwmY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsXRwmY.gif&h=ea7f14ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"818e48b519d46d7db49669357c1f14690ec095ad","tid":2438352,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"如果有人打bnt出事，佢地會急急腳停左打bnt架啦"}]}